content:
It&rsquo;s quite unnerving sometime on what you stumble upon on the internet. In today&rsquo;s world of music where lyrics mean nothing some just keep it alive. This is a post on what I just stumbled upon - this beautiful song, if you ever struggled or ever been through your downside of life or you are now feeling low, this a beautiful song that can touch your soul. Yep, music touches your soul like love does. Sometimes when I&rsquo;m sad or depressed I just play loud music with my headphone (noise cancelling üòÑ) on and sleep. This is a great way or only way that helps me get over alot of sadness in life. Grateful for alot of things that I have in my life while these beautiful emotions that touches your soul - sadness, difficulty, music and love has only made me a better and stronger person today.

Isn&rsquo;t it true : &ldquo;God only knows what you&rsquo;ve been through  God only knows what they say about you  God only knows how it&rsquo;s killing you  But there&rsquo;s a kind of love that God only knows  God only knows the real you&rdquo;
Hope this song helps you, makes your day better and put a damn smile on that face. #Loveyouself #StayStrong #GodOnlyKnows
Oh!! by the way if you need hope &amp; you just haven&rsquo;t seen it yet, here you go&hellip; this is a beautiful song too&hellip;
